1) Download Ubuntu Source code

2)Gather Libraries
	
OpenGL-GLUT-Mesa3.4 - sudo apt-get install freeglut3-dev

Libjpeg - sudo apt-get install libjpeg-dev

Libjpng - sudo apt-get install libpng-dev

3) Install linux libraries

Build-Essential - sudo apt-get install build-essential

auto-make - sudo apt-get install automake

4) Install GTK libraries

gtkglext - sudo apt-get install libgtkglext1-dev

5) Download LUA 5.3 source code
	download readline dependency - sudo apt-get install libreadline-dev
	run - "make Linux" while in Lua directory (Ex: Home/Downloads/Lua5.3.5)
	run- "make Linux install" 


6) Install autoconf/libtool
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install autoconf

sudo apt-get install libtool-bin


7) run - autoreconf -v -i   (not sure why)


8) run - ./configure --with-gtk
	(should return with "celestia configuration complete" once completed)	


9) run ./configure --with-lua=/path/to/lua --with-gtk 

(Ex: sudo ./configure --with-lua=/home/usr/Downloads/lua-5.3.5 --with-gtk)





